metadata.name: LIFE CYCLE
metadata.description:
I want to draw attention to the fact that everything is cyclical, the market, wars, life ... unfortunately, this algorithm is not subject to us. It is fed by the energy of the sun, and as long as the sun burns, as long as it burns trillions of nuclear reactions generate this "market", everything will be cyclical ...

For this project I took 200 photos in 1 year.  

By the way, this "Chestnut" tree is a symbol of Kyiv! This tree stands in Kyiv!  

3024 × 4032
